Name: repoze.whooze
Version: 0.1
Summary: A repoze.who IAuthentication plugin for Zope 3
Home-page: http://www.repoze.org
Author: Agendaless Consulting
Author-email: repoze-dev@lists.repoze.org
License: BSD-derived (http://www.repoze.org/LICENSE.txt)
Description: An IAuthentication utility for Zope 3 that obtains authentication
        information from repoze.who.
        
        
        Changelog
        =========
        
        In next release
        
          - The ``groups`` attribute is now a dictionary with group ids
           mapping to groups. The authentication framework expects it to be an
           iterable that yields the group id.
        
          - Fire event upon creation of who principal.
        
        0.1
        
          Initial release.
        
        
